milestones.description: Habibul Bashar and Rajin Saleh's 82-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 59 between Mehrab Hossain and Al Sahariar

stories.title: Youhana century steers Pakistan to 74-run win
stories.summary: Three quick wickets from Shoaib Malik, including that of the dangerous Rajin Saleh, allowed Pakistan to smother Bangladesh's gutsy attempt to chase down 243, and emerge victors by 74 runs in the second one-day international at Faisalabad
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by Chandrahas Choudhury
